Package: hExplorer
Type: Package
Title: Hurricane Plotter and Analyzer for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Cao", email = 'yc849@cornell.edu', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
    person("Aristotle", "Kolefas", email = 'aak99@cornell.edu', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yc849@cornell.edu>
Description: Analyzes and plots hurricane data from 
  \url{https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Data_Storm.html}. 
  Produces plots of the trajectory of each storm, estimates its position at
  arbitrary time points, and determines its approximate shape.
